import { Flex, Spacer, Box, ButtonGroup, Button, Heading } from '@chakra-ui/react'

function Footer() {
    return (
        <Flex 
            minWidth='max-content'
            flexDirection='column'
            justifyContent='space-evenly'
            alignItems='center'
            bg='#131313'
            p='4'
        >
        <Box p='1'>
            <Heading size='4x3'>
                BreakDown
            </Heading>
        </Box>
        </Flex>
    )
}

export default Footer;
